{"tid":1928802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男生「越帥」就不用怕武漢肺炎？芬蘭研究：自體免疫力比一般人高","createTime":"2020-03-16T14:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T16:33:26.000Z","uid":3189,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1bde9347a5aad273f98ab8cac543414f6c710f","tid":1928802,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:52:46.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐，世界各國政府繃緊神經提高戒備，民眾瘋搶口罩人人自危。近日芬蘭土庫大學（Turku）公布一項研究報告指出，男生長相樣貌越帥，自體免疫力比一般人高，較不容易生病，再度掀起話題。<br />\n<br />\n芬蘭土庫大學教授馬克思（Markus J. Rantala）在最新一期的英國研究期刊發表，指出男性長相俊俏、身材越完美，體內的「睪丸激素」水準較高，因而助於提升免疫力。<br />\n<br />\n不過，這項研究只有男性適用！該研究也發現，女性體態勻稱體脂適中，血液中的「皮質醇」濃度較低，雖然提高生育能力，但免疫力並不會比較好。而女性腰圍越粗，早死的風險越高，容易中風等心血管疾病。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://style.udn.com/style/story/8090/4322890\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstyle.udn.com%2Fstyle%2Fstory%2F8090%2F4322890&d=eokTwrWYlXUgHXHl4H%2Bebf3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=4cd501d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://style.udn.com/style/story/8090/4322890</a>"},{"pid":"6fa74ba563662204757158585b0cd32969836997","tid":1928802,"uid":301989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5523b1e3b4ff6bf7655c9dddf94eb3d6cf71d3","tid":1928802,"uid":28720,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:54:15.000Z","msg":"鬆一口氣了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"921c199a8b96e893dfbcafa816cc413ad4efb918","tid":1928802,"uid":39492,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T14:55:01.000Z","msg":"樣衰就係原罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5912a017a0abc58bd1759b0bce9f4903ea15c3c6","tid":1928802,"uid":15823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0